The revised budget for the Extraordinary Chambers in the Courts of Cambodia (ECCC) for the period 2014-2015 has been approved, and is now available on the ECCC website.
The revised budget for the year 2015 totals US$33.8 million, of which US$27.1 million is for the international component and US$6.7 million is for the national component.
The budget for 2014 was revised on the basis of expenditures of US$27.8 million, of which US$ 21.7 million were  expenditures incurred by the international component and expenditures of US$ 6.1 million by the national component.  